Name: AutoGUIX
Version: 0.0.4
Summary: AutoGUIX is the extended version of PyAutoGUI. Few features are added with the help of PyGetWindow and PyAutoGUI.
Home-page: https://github.com/4akhilkumar/autoguix
Author: Sai Akhil Kumar Reddy N
